Package: dcast3
Title: Epidemic Nowcasting via Censored Regression (RTMB Engine)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Rodrigo", "Zepeda", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "noreply@example.com")
Description: A cmdstanr-free reimplementation of the diseasenowcast2
    nowcasting model using RTMB (CppAD autodiff + a built-in Laplace
    approximation for the latent epidemic process). Reproduces the model
    menu, model(likelihood(), epidemic(), delay()), and the two-stage
    multiple-imputation nowcast, but with no Stan dependency. The reporting
    delay is modelled directly as a stochastic process, jointly with the
    epidemic dynamics, via the Guenther et al. (2021) censored likelihood.
